				</div>

				<div class="imgs-caption serif-360-caption">
					<p class="img-caption-text front show">Seen from the front, SERIF TV is defined by a single frame, one colour, one shape. Available in white, dark blue and red.</p>
					<p class="img-caption-text side">The design of the ‘I’ shape means it can stand seamlessly in the home by resting on its own base.</p>
					<p class="img-caption-text back">A woven fabric panel, designed to emulate the effect of curtain mode, elegantly conceals the connectors on the back of the television.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
