			</div>
			<div class="grid-text left">
				<div class="imgs-caption with-legs-caption">
					<p class="img-caption-text">SERIF TV moves away from the logic of ultra thin screens. Its presence is like an object; you can turn around and manipulate it. It can stand anywhere – even on the floor using the legs.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>


<!-- SECTION: REMOTE -->
