					<p class="img-caption-text">Most of the time, design is not about inventing functions but making them simple and accessible. The Bouroullec brothers adopted this approach when re-designing the existing Samsung TV software, to create a bespoke user interface and remote control.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>


